                    <div class="highlight-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="40px" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="40px" fill="#000000"><path d="m385.67-412 35.66-114.67-94-74h115.34L480-717.33l36.67 116.66h116l-94.34 74 35 114.67L480-483l-94.33 71Zm-143 372v-305.67Q200-391 180-446.33 160-501.67 160-560q0-135.33 92.33-227.67Q344.67-880 480-880q135.33 0 227.67 92.33Q800-695.33 800-560q0 58.33-20 113.67-20 55.33-62.67 100.66V-40L480-119.33 242.67-40Zm417-340.33Q733.33-454 733.33-560q0-106-73.66-179.67Q586-813.33 480-813.33q-106 0-179.67 73.66Q226.67-666 226.67-560q0 106 73.66 179.67Q374-306.67 480-306.67q106 0 179.67-73.66ZM309.33-135.67 480-186l170.67 50.33V-291q-38.34 26-82.5 38.5Q524-240 480-240t-88.17-12.5q-44.16-12.5-82.5-38.5v155.33Zm170.67-78Z"/></svg></div>
